text: Compound of six octahedra has two form. one form is a symmetric arrangement of 6 octahedra, considered as square bipyramid. It is a dual of a special case of the compound of 6 cubes with rotational freedom Another form is a dual of another compound of six cubes ==See also== *Compound of three octahedra *Compound of five octahedra *Compound of four octahedra *Compound of six cubes == References == * Octahedron6-Compound Category:Polyhedral compounds
title: Compound of six octahedra
